data.body:
- removed some redundant code & comments;
- make EAGLView a root view of RootViewController instead of subview;
- added missed `bridge` casts;

Also, few proposals:
- do some actions in `viewDidDisappear` & `viewWillAppear` (when new ViewController is pushed). E.g. pause/resume the game, so open GL view is not used while it's not visible;
- rename `RootViewController` to `CocosViewController`;
- extract multi touch setting into cocos side;
